name: AudioEffectBandPassFilter

name: AudioEffectDistortion
description: Adds a distortion audio effect to an Audio bus. Modify the sound to make it dirty.

name: AudioEffectEQ
description: Base class for audio equalizers. Gives you control over frequencies. Use it to create a custom equalizer if [AudioEffectEQ6], [AudioEffectEQ10] or [AudioEffectEQ21] don't fit your needs.

name: AudioEffectEQ10
description: Adds a 10-band equalizer audio effect to an Audio bus. Gives you control over frequencies from 31 Hz to 16000 Hz. Each frequency can be modulated between -60/+24 dB.

name: AudioEffectEQ21
description: Adds a 21-band equalizer audio effect to an Audio bus. Gives you control over frequencies from 22 Hz to 22000 Hz. Each frequency can be modulated between -60/+24 dB.

name: AudioEffectEQ6
description: Adds a 6-band equalizer audio effect to an Audio bus. Gives you control over frequencies from 32 Hz to 10000 Hz. Each frequency can be modulated between -60/+24 dB.

name: AudioEffectFilter
description: Adds a filter to the audio bus.

name: AudioEffectHighPassFilter
description: Adds a high-pass filter to the Audio Bus.

name: AudioEffectLimiter
description: Adds a soft-clip limiter audio effect to an Audio bus.

name: AudioEffectLowPassFilter
description: Adds a low-pass filter to the Audio bus.

name: AudioEffectNotchFilter
description: Adds a notch filter to the Audio bus.

name: AudioEffectPanner
description: Adds a panner audio effect to an Audio bus. Pans sound left or right.

name: AudioEffectPhaser
description: Adds a phaser audio effect to an Audio bus. Combines the original signal with a copy that is slightly out of phase with the original.

name: AudioEffectPitchShift
description: Adds a pitch-shifting audio effect to an Audio bus. Raises or lowers the pitch of original sound.

name: AudioEffectReverb
description: Adds a reverberation audio effect to an Audio bus. Simulates the sound of acoustic environments such as rooms, concert halls, caverns, or an open spaces.
